metadata.name: "Cuffed” | SQUARE1 #1
metadata.description:
"Cuffed” | SQUARE1 #1 | VR Abstract Oil Painting | NFT Art 

Good vibes only.

A VR Abstract Art Piece Created using OpenBrush with the Oculus Quest 2 2

After purchasing you will get Tilt Brush/OpenBrush's .tilt file, a packed .GLTF file, and Blender's .blend file to view on your VR set or 3D application of your choice.
